---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="code" color="#48769e" size="2.5rem" />
		<h2>Data-driven communications</h2>
		<p>SQL, Python and BI tools (Power BI, Tableau) applied to communications strategy — because data without narrative doesn't drive change.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="#48769e" size="2.5rem" />
		<h2>AI Ethics</h2>
		<p>Rights-based approach to AI ethics — from fundamental rights impact assessments (FRIA) under the EU AI Act to algorithmic bias analysis. Applying human rights frameworks where it matters most: the effect of AI systems on people.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="#48769e" size="2.5rem" />
		<h2>Business Insights</h2>
		<p>Translating data into decisions that move stakeholders — from EU funding agencies to executive teams, across international cooperation, human rights and SaaS environments. Including workshop facilitation and AI literacy training for non-technical audiences.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid #48769e;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
		font-family: var(--font-brand);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-300);
		font-family: var(--font-body);
	}

	:global(.theme-dark) .skills p {
		color: #c4aaa0;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
